Message: I don't believe a single human lives without secrets. We all have something to hide.
I would have liked to tell you something like : ''It's okay, there just wasn't any satisfying blackmailing material''. But I wouldn't have believed it myself.

Possible Answers: So? Will you leave me alone now?

Message: Unfortunately, I'm not letting you go for now. I still believe you can be of use to me.
Sorry. Whether you're okay with it or not, we'll proceed with the next step. A slightly more serious one.
I will contact you in a few hours.
